    <div class='row'>
      <h3>Design Objective</h3>
      <p>
        To create a clear, conversion-friendly
        <strong>e-commerce shopping experience</strong>
        for an outdoor jacket brand—focusing on strong hierarchy, confident calls-to-action, and a
        smooth path from
        <strong>product discovery</strong>
        to
        <strong>checkout success</strong>. The goal was a design that feels reliable and easy to use
        across devices.
      </p>
