          <div class='case-study-text'>
            <h3>Concept &amp; Visual Direction</h3>
            <ul class='bullet-list'>
              <li>
                Built a clean, outdoorsy tone with a focus on
                <strong>trust</strong>
                and
                <strong>clarity</strong>
                (simple layout, readable typography, calm spacing)
              </li>
              <li>
                Designed a product presentation system that supports quick scanning:
                <strong>consistent cards</strong>, clear pricing, and strong CTAs
              </li>
              <li>
                Kept the interface intentionally minimal so the jackets remain the main visual focus
              </li>
            </ul>
